      "source": [
        "Online food delivery platforms generate a vast amount of restaurant-related data, including customer ratings, reviews, cuisines, pricing, location, online delivery availability, and table booking information. Customers often rely on restaurant ratings to make dining decisions, while restaurant owners use these ratings to evaluate and improve their services. However, restaurant ratings are influenced by multiple factors, making it difficult to determine how each feature contributes to the overall rating.\n",
