    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "The project consists of two datasets: the **Zomato Restaurant Metadata** dataset and the **Zomato Restaurant Reviews** dataset. The metadata dataset contains restaurant-related information such as restaurant name, links, cost, collections, cuisines, and timings, while the reviews dataset contains customer reviews along with reviewer details, ratings, review metadata, review time, and pictures.\n",
